%S A393729 1,1,3,12,61,398,2942,23264,192082,1633909,14217048,126001912
%N A393729 Number of free polyominoes in the {6,4} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%F A393729 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q; also P{p,q}(q+1) = P{p,oo}(q+1) + floor((p-1)/2) - floor((3+q(p-2))/2). In this case, p=6, q=4 and P{p,oo} = A004127.
%o A393729 (C) // See A393739.
%Y A393729 Cf. A393730, A393731, A393732, A393733, A004127.
%K A393729 nonn,more,changed
